title: Cueto tosses gem as Royals beat Astros 7-2 in ALDS clincher (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,278 Cueto tosses gem as Royals beat Astros 7-2 in ALDS clincher (Yahoo Sports) Johnny Cueto delivered a masterpiece on his biggest stage yet, pitching eight dominant innings Wednesday night and leading the resilient Kansas City Royals to a 7-2 victory over the Houston Astros and back to the American League Championship Series. Cueto allowed two hits, a single by Evan Gattis followed by Luis Valbuena's second-inning homer, before retiring the final 19 batters he faced. When Wade Davis breezed through the ninth, the Royals poured onto the field to celebrate.
